s). Found loaded on disk under WorldMirror-V2/ but entirely missing from the original 5-model baseline scope.\nKnown Limitations: No native ComfyUI support -- requires this specific community custom node pack. No official example workflow JSON exists to fetch verbatim; this baseline is a best-effort transcription of the documented node graph, NOT a downloaded official file. Flag for manual verification against the actual installed node pack's parameter names once loaded in ComfyUI.\nVerified: NO ƒ?\" pending load test in ComfyUI (Phase 3, next window). EXTRA CAUTION: also pending confirmation that node names/widget order match the installed version of cedarconnor/ComfyUI-HunyuanWorld-Mirror exactly, since this JSON was hand-built rather than fetched.\n\r\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
